mercurial-recipe
================

This is a mercurial recipe for buildout.
Previous version by Tim Molendijk is registered with pip.
So to use one need to download it and add directory to develope section in buildout.cfg.
i.e.:

  [buildout]
  extensions = buildout.dumppickedversions
  develop = ../mercurial-recipe
          .
  extra-paths =


Changes introduced in comparision to baseline
---------------------------------------------
- support for specific revision using rev option
- support for egg creation using as_egg option
